Server init.
>> a := Blob new: 4.
a bytes: ( List new ; Bin b00000101 ; Hx x0A ; Bin b10000001 ; 0).
>> b := Blob new: 4.
b bytes: ( List new ; Bin b00000110 ; Hx x0A ; Bin b10000000 ; 0).
Vault xor: a and: b.
# >> c := a new. @todo fix memory leak, Blob new should not be allowed.
# Vault xor: a and: c. # should not be possible
{
	Vault
		xor: ( File new: ['noblob???'] ) 
		and: ( File new: ['noblob???'] ).
} except: { :e Out write: e, stop. }, start.
a free.
b free.
